Ex-Glee star and convicted pedophile Mark Sailing has died following a reported suicide according to TMZ, US Weekly and The Hollywood Reporter. His body was found on Tuesday in a riverbed near his home in Los Angeles. He was 35 years old. Salling played Noah "Puck" Puckerman on the hit Fox musical dramedy Glee from 2009 until 2015 . In December 2015 he was arrested for being in possession of child pornography. The actor pleaded guilty in December last year and was awaiting sentencing. Source: Channel24